long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Perfect for social media managers, researchers, and data enthusiasts. TwListExport streamlines your Twitter/X list management and analysis.

ğŸ“¦ What You Can Export:
1. Followers of a List
2. Members of a List

ğŸŒŸKey Features:
â€¢ One-click export to CSV
â€¢ Smart rate limit handling - no user action required
â€¢ Export history tracking
â€¢ Resume interrupted exports
â€¢ Regenerate CSV from previous exports

ğŸ“‹The exported CSV file includes these columns:
  Basic Info:
    - Handle, Name, Bio
    - Account creation date, Location
    - Verification status (Legacy and Twitter Blue)  
  Engagement Metrics:
    - Followers count, Following count
    - Post count, Media count
    - Total favorites by user  
  Profile Links:
    - User page URL
    - Profile URL
    - Profile banner URL
    - Avatar URL  
  Additional Data:
    - Tweet ID
    - DM availability

ğŸ”’ Data Privacy:
